rows.label: xs31030100_MSG0020
rows.name:
It's pitch black-meh!
Just complete darkness-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31030100_MSG0030
rows.name:
I can't even see light beyond
where it was swallowed[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31030100_MSG0050
rows.name: It exceeds the realm of understanding[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31030100_MSG0070
rows.name:
Even if that were something like a black hole,
we should be getting anomalous mass readings, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31030100_MSG0100
rows.name: First, let's prioritize the evacuation of nearby squad members.[ST:wait ]
